data.description: You have got to check out this awesome 3 bedroom with an office, home. It is move in ready. Located in a nice, quiet neighborhood which is close to schools and stores but not so close you feel like you are in town. The home has just been painted inside and out, carpets have been cleaned and the open floorpan is amazing for family and friends to enjoy. The vaulted ceiling in the open kitchen, family room and formal dining room allow an abundance of natural light to fill the space. The master bedroom is large and has access to the office which could also be used as a media room, baby room or kids play room. That's what is so great about it, you can make it whatever fits your needs. You have got to see this home. Call today to schedule your showing before it is gone. You will be glad that you did.
